{"tid":1965630,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"確診男警長情況轉差　入ICU需插喉","createTime":"2020-04-09T14:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T16:08:44.000Z","uid":20933,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8db96e27597255157ce04f64ae304024d3854832","tid":1965630,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:57:14.000Z","msg":"本報綜合三個消息得悉，上周六（4日）確診感染新型冠狀病毒的46歲西九龍總區機動部隊男警長，今日（9日）入夜後情況轉差，開始出現呼吸困難，需插喉治療，目前已轉入在伊利沙伯醫院深切治療部留醫。據了解，他暫未有即時生命危險。<br />\n<br />\n有消息稱，該警長因肺炎出現肺衰竭迹象，致呼吸困難。根據衛生防護中心上周六（4日）公布的資料，他並無長期病患。"},{"pid":"57903adf77148e653c82f9bda55ab7a0dbc4ac77","tid":1965630,"uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:57:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200409/s00001/1586443629535/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200409%2Fs00001%2F1586443629535%2F&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVVT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=f0dbd7e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200409%2Fs00001%2F1586443629535%2F&h=fd61e195\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200409/s00001/1586443629535/</a>"},{"pid":"a7577e41ed20085298343f440a1a7c42cf15b216","tid":1965630,"uid":70227,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:57:27.000Z","msg":"最緊要人有事"},{"pid":"47572e5e9beffaa1a2cf045addabb99114197a49","tid":1965630,"uid":118888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:57:44.000Z","msg":"黑警插全家"},{"pid":"bd3c1e0a7e28652ad2ed6588f65722ff6d5d86cc","tid":1965630,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:57:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85ed695e38ff90d5c73480d92bdd2514f4475d20","tid":1965630,"uid":307329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T